<p>As always, the food was high on my list and there is a great restaurant in-house. Breakfast is only available to guests and there is a wonderful choice of a buffet or a cook to order menu.</p>

<div class="row no-gutters">
    <div class="col-md-6 col-sm-12">
        <div class="post-left-image" style="background: url(../images/malta/Palais-Le-Brun/Palais-Le-Brun-17.jpg) no-repeat; background-size: cover; margin-right: 0.5rem; max-height: 600px !important"></div>
